4. Evaluate sensor behavior on curved surfaces similar to human fingertips

 Test if the sensor works when wrapped around a finger (the actual use case).

via:

    Mount the sensor on curved surfaces of different radii:

        Small radius (finger tip ~10mm)

        Medium radius (finger pad ~20mm)

        Large radius (palm ~50mm)

    Test with the sensor:

        Flat (baseline)

        Slightly curved

        Highly curved (wrapped around a tube)

        With adhesive backing

        Without adhesive



Curvature          | ADC no touch | ADC light | ADC hard | Repeatability
-------------------|--------------|-----------|----------|---------------
Flat (baseline)    | 4            | 500       | 3500     | Good
Slight curve       | 6            | 550       | 3400     | Good
Finger-like curve  | 10           | 600       | 3200     | Moderate
Tight curve        | 15           | 700       | 2800     | Poor

